          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 611,
          "y_px": -762
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-4",
        "text": "Nicholas Snyder",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 16
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 28,
          "y_px": -674
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-5",
        "text": "A humble wall of ironstone had here long played a key role in this city&apos;s function.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 18,
          "y_px": -538
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-6",
        "text": "At half the height of the opposing wall of granite and holding back the same",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": -504
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-7",
        "text": "embankment, it did twice the work, until it could do it no more. In 2018 came",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 2,
          "y_px": -472
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-8",
        "text": "unrelenting spring rains, collapse of this wall and then worrying discourse over",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 2,
          "y_px": -440
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-9",
        "text": "its viability and future.",
