          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -30,
          "y_px": -409
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-10",
        "text": "Enter a local retired engineer and a contractor with a restoration plan that",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 2,
          "y_px": -350
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-11",
        "text": "cascaded into months of fundraising, the coming together of two tenacious,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 6,
          "y_px": -316
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-12",
        "text": "aged men, an adventurous search for stones and three years of construction.",
